 <h3 class="text-2xl">Project Description</h3>
 <p>
   I am interested in the number of tweets that mention a big tech company  <a href="/apple">Apple</a>, Meta, Microsoft, Alphabet, Amazon, Tesla) and the respective stock prices of that company at that time.
My idea is that if the number of tweets mentioning one of the companies should be corelated to the respective stock prices.
 </p>
